item.title: AI Technology Is Revolutionizing CANCER Prediction Methods – Chia-Lin Simmons
item.description: Chia-Lin Simmons is the CEO of LogicMark, a company revolutionizing healthcare with AI-powered technology. Today, she reveals how AI and wearable devices are transforming elderly care and predicting health risks before they become serious. AI is reshaping the future of healthcare, making early detection and prevention more effective than ever.
